<item>
 <title>Interior Monologues</title>
 <link>https://www.mererid.co.uk/node/53</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;A group show at Oriel y Bont with many layers to it. Contributing artists responded to an artwork in the Art Collection of the University of South Wales. They also needed to provide at least 4 pages of artwork for an A5 zine to go with the show. Creative writers were assigned to each artist and wrote something in response to both the new and old work. At the exhibition opening each writer read their piece of writing. Hearing Maria Lalic read the text she wrote in response to my work and our conversations via email was a highlight for me. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Copies of the zine may still be available from Oriel y Bont.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-image field-type-image field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://www.mererid.co.uk/sites/mererid.co.uk/files/styles/large/public/blog/images/52487896_620562918363919_4891886210189885440_n.jpg?itok=Reyi0YB8&quot; width=&quot;480&quot; height=&quot;342&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
